ster</a>查找预售信息。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> SUPERCHARGED WORLDWIDE IN &#39;25 将于明年秋天与特邀嘉宾<a href="https://twitter.com/simpleplan?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@simpleplan</a>一起来到欧洲和英国<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26a1.png" alt="⚡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>门票于当地时间 10 月 18 日星期五上午 10 点开始发售。</p><p> ...更多日期即将到来！ <a href="https://t.co/q3TpxOZyzB">pic.twitter.com/q3TpxOZyzB</a></p><p> — 后代 (@offspring) <a href="https://twitter.com/offspring/status/1845736308242858256?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 10 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> The Offspring 还将在 2025 年 9 月下旬至 11 月初在欧洲各地演出（ <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/the-offspring-tickets/artist/753206?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=Q1P3Mi3O8xyKReU1H3SOpzJrUkCRTI2hGVn6y80&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请在此处购买门票</a>）。他们承诺“未来还会有更多约会”，作为即将到来的“全球”巡演的一部分。</p><h3> <strong>The Offspring 2025 年英国“Supercharged”巡演日期为：</strong></h3><p><strong>十一月</strong><br /><strong>10 – 卡迪夫Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>14 – O2，伦敦</strong><br /><strong>15 - 纽卡斯尔Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>16 - AO 竞技场，曼彻斯特</strong><br /><strong>18 – OVO Hydro，格拉斯哥</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-offspring-interview-supercharged-yungblud-ed-sheeran-brian-may-future-3795527" target="_blank" rel="noopener">最近，乐队在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>表示，他们“希望通过《Supercharged》制作一张典型的 Offspring 唱片”，“我认为我们已经成功了。”</p><p> Dexter Holland 和 Noodles 还向<em>NME</em>讲述了他们在新专辑中融入早期作品的情况，回忆了与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">Ed Sheeran</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">Brian May 的</a>即兴表演，并讨论了让<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">Yungblud</a>作为他们的“炒作人”。</p><p>至于是否可以尽快结束，Noodles 解释道：“我们只是在热身而已！我想继续下去，并且仍在寻找方法使其比以往任何时候都更大。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DA_Bldpz0Fs/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 5